<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l5">vnd Bertlein von Swangoẅ <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe / <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ſeyn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l6">als wır <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> haben vor etlıchen <expan>cʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> ein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> geſwornen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l7"><expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>gena<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>f<ex>riedrich</ex></expan> ʒeſel <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> vns <expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l8">vnd wır Jn <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> haben / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wır <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Göldlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l9"><expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> dem wır <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
